{"tid":2462902,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"中國女足女神趙麗娜30歲仍嫁不出，擇偶標準不高：超過1米6就行","createTime":"2021-03-26T09:43:36.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-26T09:53:37.000Z","uid":25345,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"eed93cda7e4d895dc7faecdb1b1f615bd9a42606","tid":2462902,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T09:43:36.000Z","msg":"中國女足界最美的女神，現年29歲的她仍是單身，在一次採訪中曾透露，她的擇偶標准其實很簡單，身高超過1.6米就夠了。<br />\n<br />\n  <img src=\"https://nimg.ws.126.net/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fdingyue.ws.126.net%2F2021%2F0324%2F6708cbb4j00qqgo2y000qd000gg009cp.jpg&amp;thumbnail=650x2147483647&amp;quality=80&amp;type=jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnimg.ws.126.net%2F%3Furl%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fdingyue.ws.126.net%252F2021%252F0324%252F6708cbb4j00qqgo2y000qd000gg009cp.jpg%26thumbnail%3D650x2147483647%26quality%3D80%26type%3Djpg&h=d30e1d65&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n  這個足球界的女神就是趙麗娜，1991年出生於中國上海。由於從小就身材高達，還在上小學的時候，趙麗娜就被一名足球教練選中，開始了她的足球生涯。成年後，趙麗娜的外貌也逐漸出眾起來，甚至有不少娛樂公司紛紛向她拋來橄欖枝，但卻都遭到趙麗娜的拒絕。<br />\n<img src=\"https://nimg.ws.126.net/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fdingyue.ws.126.net%2F2021%2F0324%2F73e422dfj00qqgo2z001ed000jg00dmp.jpg&amp;thumbnail=650x2147483647&amp;quality=80&amp;type=jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnimg.ws.126.net%2F%3Furl%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fdingyue.ws.126.net%252F2021%252F0324%252F73e422dfj00qqgo2z001ed000jg00dmp.jpg%26thumbnail%3D650x2147483647%26quality%3D80%26type%3Djpg&h=0ea6cd2d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n  <br />\n<br />\n  2015年，24歲的趙麗娜進入了女超聯賽，並在第一個賽季獲得了賽季最佳門將的稱號。從那以後，很長一段時間裡，女超聯賽的最佳門將都被趙麗娜牢牢的握住。趙麗娜憑藉自己的實力，多次入選國家隊，為中國贏得了不少榮譽。<br />\n<br />\n  <br />\n<br />\n  值得一提的是，趙麗娜不但熱愛足球，在音樂方面也有著不錯的實力，尤其是對架子鼓有很濃厚的興趣。毫不誇張地說，足球和鼓樂對於趙麗娜來說，就是生命中的全部。只是遺憾的是，雖然趙麗娜如今已經30歲了，但她依舊還是單身一人。<br />\n<br />\n  <img src=\"https://nimg.ws.126.net/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fdingyue.ws.126.net%2F2021%2F0324%2Fdeba2786j00qqgo2z000ld000dw009ap.jpg&amp;thumbnail=650x2147483647&amp;quality=80&amp;type=jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnimg.ws.126.net%2F%3Furl%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fdingyue.ws.126.net%252F2021%252F0324%252Fdeba2786j00qqgo2z000ld000dw009ap.jpg%26thumbnail%3D650x2147483647%26quality%3D80%26type%3Djpg&h=cd009d13&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n  有人覺得，是不是她的擇偶標準太高了，所以誰都看不上。但是趙麗娜卻在某次採訪中表示，對於配偶的要求並不高，自己長得比較高，所以對男生的身高的要求不高，只要超過1.6米就夠了。網友們得知後紛紛表示，這簡直就是沒有要求啊，畢竟不到1.6米的男生，還是很少的。<br />\n<img src=\"http://image.uc.cn/s/wemedia/s/upload/2020/4dcf59e187329b3d0b221c67b97d63ca.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimage.uc.cn%2Fs%2Fwemedia%2Fs%2Fupload%2F2020%2F4dcf59e187329b3d0b221c67b97d63ca.jpg&h=fad26175&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n  <br />\n<br />\n  也有不少人聽到趙麗娜的擇偶標准後，都表示很心動。當然了，人家也只是隨口這麼一說，標準肯定還是有的，至少也要和她門當戶對。最後我們也希望趙麗娜能早日找到屬於自己的愛情，在生活中不再孤獨。"},{"pid":"b6616709fe487288109f91436a9c8f4aae9cecf6","tid":2462902,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T09:46:24.000Z","msg":"想識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab0465faa1c38c5d488fdc2ebe5507b9a7c9ee3d","tid":2462902,"uid":300782,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T09:47:46.000Z","msg":"屌你<br />\n著NIKE<br />\n反新彊<br />\n<br />\n支那G"},{"pid":"6750a8b306e9f3f64edd229c218fc638daa4dc30","tid":2462902,"uid":384040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b6616709fe487288109f91436a9c8f4aae9cecf6","tid":2462902,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T09:46:24.000Z","msg":"想識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T09:48:26.000Z","msg":"排隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ace97c24a4761e829f1089ddb23d3c7dfe80e09f","tid":2462902,"uid":137999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T09:49:46.000Z","msg":"想識<br />\n話晒同我同行"},{"pid":"44bfb0828e6d469f21a2cddfaf9d888c3a195d61","tid":2462902,"uid":294121,"like":1,"dislik